</figcaption>
</figure>
</p> <p>This is a fight Milibandâs party will only win if itâs bold. At stake are fairness and decency â and weâll never achieve either in a country as unequal as Britain.</p> <p>The heavies guarding the Tory super-rich tonight shows they feel threatened. Big business shouts and writes cheques to the Tories because it hates being held to account. Tough.</p> <p>Itâs time fatcats stopped dodging tax and were forced to pay living wages. Workers, the self-employed and small businesses should be on Labourâs side. Responsible large businesses, too.</p> <p>Turning a hotel into a fortress to protect Tory donors is the gulf between Camâs cronies and the rest of Britain.</p> <p> <div class="ampp3dContent">
<style>
.ampp3dContent {width: 500px;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;}
.ampp3dMessage {background:#000000 url(http://s3.mirror.co.uk/mirror/ampp3d/2015/January/28/political-faces/countdown-bg.jpg) 50% 0 no-repeat;background-size:cover;}
.ampp3dMessage h3 {padding: 25% 0 5% 0;text-align:center;color:#ffffff !important; z-index:999 !important;}
</style>
<div class="ampp3dMessage">
<h3><span class="ammp3dcountdown" data-string-date="2015/05/07 07:00:00 UTC+0100"></span></h3>
</div>
</div>
<script src="http://s3.mirror.co.uk/mirror/ampp3d/2015/January/28/political-faces/countdown.js"></script>
</p>
</div>
